### Update Category Meta
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description for Electronics category.",
  "seo-title": "Electronics - Updated SEO Title",
  "seo-description": "Updated SEO description for electronics category page."
}

###

### Update Meta - Clear SEO fields (set to null)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Only description remains."
}

###

### Update Meta - Category not found (expects 404)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/9999/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "This should fail."
}
